{"tid":1998343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華機迷求小粉紅停襲Steam","createTime":"2020-05-02T10:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T10:34:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd58e03491f7dbaa6288930a88912641988c5280","tid":1998343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200422/A4ANCXCWB6BHDE6UGZO5TF7HTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200422%2FA4ANCXCWB6BHDE6UGZO5TF7HTI%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayuffsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=5adf2490\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200422%2FA4ANCXCWB6BHDE6UGZO5TF7HTI%2F&h=518a92ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200422/A4ANCXCWB6BHDE6UGZO5TF7HTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n華機迷求小粉紅停襲Steam<br />\n<br />\n中國小粉紅再陷進退兩難的困境。有中國愛國網民發現電腦遊戲平台Steam所用的地圖多處「出錯」，要求Steam「改正」，但部份玩家擔心，自己使用多年的遊戲平台會在中國全面被禁，要求小粉紅停止出征，「我求求你們了，別亂搞了，你們這個毒的，那個毒的！」台灣有網民指有鑑於此，要代為出征，號召網友協助小粉紅向中國政府檢舉Steam。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200422/large/1587483984_6387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200422%2Flarge%2F1587483984_6387.jpg&h=05b2e112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒改圖揶揄中國玩家不應玩辱國遊戲平台。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台網民請纓代小粉紅出征<br />\n<br />\n繼早前Switch遊戲「動物森友會」在中國被禁，中國人民或再失去一個重要遊戲平台。有「愛國」網民指Steam分裂中國，用上錯誤的地圖，藏南地區的邊界出錯，台灣未與中國大陸同色，而選擇「國家/地區」時，香港和台灣都沒有加上中國，令人誤會港獨和台獨，他指各平台和組織要「尊重中國的主權和領土完整」。微博也迅速出現「#Steam辱華」標籤，不少人稱要出征，讓Steam承認「一個中國」。<br />\n<br />\n但有中國玩家哀求小紅粉手下留情， 「Steam是一個遊戲平台，我求求你們了」，台灣網民得悉後就表示「這次換我們來幫助他們出征」，號召其他人一起到中國互聯網信息辦公室檢舉Steam分裂中國，要求中國政府把Steam禁掉。早前因中國封禁「動物森友會」時，遭中國網民痛罵為罪魁禍首的黃之鋒，都再次改圖，挪揄小粉紅。但仍有中國網民表示，「出征吧，Steam權衡下就知道了，然後就把灣灣改回中國台灣地區了 」。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"0620c01451df2e0515bae1d5f64bcd8eaad36452","tid":1998343,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayuffsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=246e5802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"f4d61c8f3635c45e9505b18c48e5f79b20339479","tid":1998343,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國家面前無遊戲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黨要求你玩咩就玩咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />steam 咁多血腥暴力既遊戲點可以玩，e.g. gta 5,要玩就玩和平精英"},{"pid":"835ee7223e3f3f74437dc63ab534b25efa655c09","tid":1998343,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"出征吧，Steam權衡下就知道了，然後就把灣灣改回中國台灣地區了 」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68acb0a3e6562a2534e34b358f4c78c9f97a995","tid":1998343,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"打返強國遊戲咪幾好囉 ! 強國那麼強大, 怎會沒有好遊戲 ? 不妨問下 緊爽哥 &amp; 華大媽有咩推介啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}